<div class='box2_7 floatl m brdr'>
 <h1>Regional</h1>
      <h2>India </h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="http://www.cricinfo.com/india/content/team/6.html">CricInfo:   India</a> - Comprehensive coverage of Indian domestic and international cricket. </li>
          <li><a href="http://www.cricketpulse.com/">Cricket Pulse</a> - Find articles,   player profiles, statistics on Indian tournaments including IPL , ICL and Ranji   trophy. </li>
          <li><a href="http://cricket.deepthi.com/">Cricket.Deepthi.com</a> - Website   devoted to India cricket matches. Includes News, live scores, schedules, past   and present series statistics, and photographs. </li>
          <li><a href="http://www.cricketfundas.com/">Cricketfundas.com</a> - Includes   articles, match updates, news, cricket jokes, and trivia. </li>
          <li><a href="http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sphome/4719161.cms">India Cricket   Schedule</a> - Maintaining upcoming and current year India Cricket Series   Schedules. </li>
          <li><a href="http://www.indiatwenty20.com/">India Twenty20</a> - Collection of   articles, schedule, history of the game, rules and links to related news   stories. </li>
          <li><a href="http://cricket.123india.com/">123india.com: Cricket</a> - Features   live scorecard and voice commentary. Covers latest tour news of India and other   countries. </li>
          <li><a href="http://indiacricket.rivals.net/">Indian Cricket</a> - Includes   coverage of matches, news, previews, statistics and players. </li>
          <li><a href="http://icdiscussion.proboards23.com/">Indian Cricket   Discussion.</a> - A discussion room, for Indian cricket. </li>
          <li><a href="http://www.indiancricketfans.com/">Indian Cricket Fans</a> -   Features a forum, blogs, videos and cartoons for Indian cricket fans. </li>
          <li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thirunavukkarasu_Kumaran">Kumaran's Pages of Wickets</a> - Includes the game, players, profiles, photographs,   grounds and links. </li>
          <li><a href="http://third-umpire.blogspot.com/">thirdumpire.com</a> - Cricket weblog,   reviews and articles. </li>
          <li><a href="http://cricket.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/?">Times of India:   Cricket</a> - Features scores, match updates, schedules, news, photos, and   screen savers. </li>
          <li><a href="http://twenty20league.blogspot.com/">Twenty 20 Cricket Leagues</a> - Features match wise scorecards, television ads and promotional videos. </li>
          <li><a href="http://thevictortrumpercricketboard.yuku.com/">The Victor Trumper   Cricket Board</a> - Cricket message board, all Test playing nations catered for   especially India. </li>
          <li><a href="http://sports.dir.groups.yahoo.com/dir/Recreation___Sports/Sports/Cricket/By_Location/Countries/India">Yahoo!   Sports Groups - Cricket: India</a> - Directory of cricket clubs and fan groups   which include message forums, chats, newsletters and photo galleries. </li>
          <li><a href="http://cricket.zeenews.com/crichistory.asp?nid=76">Zee News:   History of Indian Cricket</a> - A detailed history of Indian cricket before   1930. </li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Pakistan</h2>
      <ul>
         <li><a href="http://www.cricinfo.com/pakistan/content/team/7.html">CricInfo -   Pakistan</a> - Provides statistics, news and information about players and   matches. </li>
         <li><a href="http://www.freewebs.com/pakicricket/">PakiCricket</a> - Pictures   and player profiles. </li>
         <li><a href="http://www.pakistan-cricket.com/">Pakistan-Cricket.com</a> - Fan   site devoted to cricket in Pakistan. </li>
         <li><a href="http://www.pakpassion.net/">PakPassion</a> - Features news, views,   reports and discussion forum. </li>
         <li><a href="http://pakistancricket.rivals.net/">Pakpassion</a> - Independent   fan site with news and results of the Pakistani cricket team. Also includes a   message board. </li>
         <li><a href="http://www.rlca.com.pk/">Rashid Latif Cricket Academy</a> - A   non-profit cricket academy to develop young talents. </li>
         <li><a href="http://rashidlatif.8k.com/">Rashid Latif's Home Page</a> -   Primarily concerned with the allegations of match fixing in the Pakistan Team.   </li>
         <li><a href="http://sports.dir.groups.yahoo.com/dir/Recreation___Sports/Sports/Cricket/By_Location/Countries/Pakistan">Yahoo!   Sports Groups - Cricket: Pakistan</a> - Directory of cricket clubs and fan   groups which include message forums, chats, newsletters and photo galleries. </li>
            </ul>
            <h2>Sri Lanka </h2>
            <ul>
              <li><a href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/cricket/other_international/sri_lanka/default.stm">BBC   Sri Lanka cricket</a> - BBC Sri Lankan Cricket page </li>
              <li><a href="http://www.slcricket.com/">Cricket Forum</a> - A fan site for Sri   Lanka cricket. It includes discussions, videos and much more concerning Sri   Lanka cricket. </li>
              <li><a href="http://dilmahforum.cricinfo.com/">Dilmah Forum</a> - A forum for   Sri Lanka cricket </li>
              <li><a href="http://www.cricinfo.com/srilanka/content/team/8.html">Sri Lankan   Cricket</a> - Comprehensive coverage of Sri Lankan domestic and international   cricket from CricInfo. </li>
              <li><a href="http://www.hilalscricket.com/">Where the Lions fans gather</a> -   The inside scoop on Sri Lankan Cricket. Features rare photos, Videos and   articles from the past and present. </li>
              <li><a href="http://sports.dir.groups.yahoo.com/dir/Recreation___Sports/Sports/Cricket/By_Location/Countries/Sri_Lanka">Yahoo!   Sports Groups - Cricket: Sri Lanka</a> - Directory of cricket clubs and fan   groups which include message forums, chats, newsletters and photo galleries.</li>
              </ul>
              <h2>West Indes </h2>
      <ul> <li><a href="http://www.caribbeancricket.com/">CaribbeanCricket</a> - Includes news, commentary and discussion for the sport in the West Indies and the  Caribbean. </li>
       <li><a href="http://www.cricinfo.com/westindies/content/team/4.html">CricInfo -   West Indies</a> - Includes coverage of the sport both domestic and   international. </li>
       <li><a href="http://www.windiescricket.com/">West Indies Cricket Board</a> -   Official site of the governing body for the sport in West Indies. Includes   international and domestic news and articles. </li>
      </ul>
